body:
 - Fix up links;
 - Drop _frequently updated_ warning, etc.

Signed-off-by: Gao Xiang <hsiangkao@linux.alibaba.com>

If prefetch_config.enable = true, prefetch all data after open data blob.

tested with a configuration json like below:
```
{
  "type": "bootstrap",
  "config": {
    "backend_type": "registry",
    "backend_config": {
      "scheme": "https"
    },
    "cache_type": "fscache"
  },
  "fs_prefetch": {
    "enable": true,
    "threads_count": 2,
    "merging_size": 131072,
    "bandwidth_rate": 0
  }
}
```
